<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="cs">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>generace.work — Rozumíme generaci, kterou potřebujete</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Pomáháme firmám najít, udržet a vést mladé zaměstnance. 15 let dat. Tisíce proškolených lidí. Nejlepší Gen Z data v Česku.">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Gabarito:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&family=Sanchez:ital@0;1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    /* ===== RESET & BASE ===== */
    *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    :root {
      --navy: #04193c;
      --red: #f0324b;
      --light-blue: #c9e8fb;
      --orange: #ffa000;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --black: #000000;
      --poly-blue: rgba(201, 232, 251, 0.4);
      --poly-stroke: rgba(201, 232, 251, 0.6);
    }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Gabarito', sans-serif;
      color: var(--navy);
      background: var(--white);
      line-height: 1.6;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    /* ===== TYPOGRAPHY ===== */
    h1, h2, h3, h4 {
      font-family: 'Gabarito', sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.15;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .accent {
      font-family: 'Sanchez', serif;
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--red);
    }

    /* ===== LAYOUT ===== */
    .container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 24px;
    }

    section {
      position: relative;
    }

    /* ===== FADE-IN ANIMATION ===== */
    /* JS adds .js-ready to html — without JS, everything is visible */
    .js-ready .fade-in {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(32px);
      transition: opacity 0.7s ease-out, transform 0.7s ease-out;
    }

    .js-ready .fade-in.visible {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    /* Stagger children */
    .js-ready .fade-in-children > * {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(24px);
      transition: opacity 0.6s ease-out, transform 0.6s ease-out;
    }

    .js-ready .fade-in-children.visible > *:nth-child(1) { transition-delay: 0s; }
    .js-ready .fade-in-children.visible > *:nth-child(2) { transition-delay: 0.12s; }
    .js-ready .fade-in-children.visible > *:nth-child(3) { transition-delay: 0.24s; }
    .js-ready .fade-in-children.visible > *:nth-child(4) { transition-delay: 0.36s; }
    .js-ready .fade-in-children.visible > *:nth-child(5) { transition-delay: 0.48s; }

    .js-ready .fade-in-children.visible > * {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    /* ===== POLYGON DECORATIONS ===== */
    .polygon {
      position: absolute;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .polygon svg {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
    }

    /* ===== SECTION DIVIDER — /// strip ===== */
    .divider {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      height: 48px;
      user-select: none;
      background: var(--white);
    }

    .divider-inner {
      font-family: 'Gabarito', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 900;
      font-size: 20px;
      letter-spacing: 6px;
      color: var(--light-blue);
      white-space: nowrap;
      line-height: 48px;
    }

    .divider--dark {
      background: var(--navy);
    }

    .divider--dark .divider-inner {
      color: rgba(201, 232, 251, 0.25);
    }

    .divider--light-blue {
      background: var(--light-blue);
    }

    .divider--light-blue .divider-inner {
      color: rgba(4, 25, 60, 0.12);
    }

    /* ===== NAV ===== */
    .nav {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      z-index: 1000;
      padding: 16px 0;
      transition: background 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s, padding 0.3s;
    }

    .nav.scrolled {
      background: rgba(4, 25, 60, 0.97);
      box-shadow: 0 2px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
      padding: 10px 0;
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    }

    .nav .container {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .nav-logo {
      font-family: 'Gabarito', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 900;
      font-size: 20px;
      color: var(--white);
      text-decoration: none;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }

    .nav-logo span {
      color: var(--red);
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: none;
      list-style: none;
      gap: 32px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.3px;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover {
      color: var(--white);
    }

    .nav-cta {
      background: var(--red);
      color: var(--white) !important;
      padding: 10px 24px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 700 !important;
      transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.2s !important;
    }

    .nav-cta:hover {
      background: var(--orange) !important;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      .nav-links {
        display: flex;
      }
    }

    /* ===== HERO ===== */
    #hero {
      background: var(--navy);
      color: var(--white);
      padding: 160px 0 100px;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    #hero .polygon-hero-1 {
      top: -80px;
      right: -120px;
      width: 400px;
      height: 400px;
    }

    #hero .polygon-hero-2 {
      bottom: -60px;
      left: -80px;
      width: 300px;
      height: 300px;
    }

    #hero .polygon-hero-3 {
      top: 30%;
      right: 5%;
      width: 200px;
      height: 200px;
    }

    .hero-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      max-width: 800px;
    }

    .hero-tag {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--red);
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .hero-content h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 4.2rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
    }

    .hero-content p {
      font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 2vw, 1.25rem);
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
      max-width: 620px;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      display: inline-block;
      background: var(--red);
      color: var(--white);
      padding: 18px 44px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.3px;
      transition: background 0.25s, transform 0.25s, box-shadow 0.25s;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: var(--orange);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(240, 50, 75, 0.3);
    }

    /* ===== PROBLEM / STATS ===== */
    #problem {
      background: var(--white);
      padding: 100px 0 110px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    #problem .polygon-stats {
      top: -40px;
      left: -60px;
      width: 250px;
      height: 250px;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    #problem .container {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .section-label {
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 4px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--red);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .section-heading {
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      margin-bottom: 60px;
      max-width: 700px;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }

    .stats-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 48px;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      .stats-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 48px;
      }
    }

    .stat-card {
      position: relative;
    }

    .stat-number {
      font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 4.5rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--navy);
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      letter-spacing: -2px;
    }

    .stat-number span {
      color: var(--red);
    }

    .stat-text {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      color: rgba(4, 25, 60, 0.7);
      line-height: 1.6;
      max-width: 320px;
    }

    /* ===== THREE PILLARS ===== */
    #pillars {
      background: var(--navy);
      color: var(--white);
      padding: 100px 0 110px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    #pillars .polygon-pillars {
      bottom: -80px;
      right: -60px;
      width: 350px;
      height: 350px;
    }

    .pillars-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      .pillars-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 48px;
      }
    }

    .pillar-card {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      padding: 40px 32px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(201, 232, 251, 0.15);
      border-radius: 12px;
      transition: border-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
    }

    .pillar-card:hover {
      border-color: rgba(201, 232, 251, 0.35);
      transform: translateY(-4px);
    }

    .pillar-number {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      color: var(--red);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .pillar-card h3 {
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      letter-spacing: -0.3px;
    }

    .pillar-card p {
      font-size: 0.98rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
    }

    /* ===== PRO KOHO ===== */
    #audience {
      background: var(--light-blue);
      padding: 100px 0 110px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    #audience .polygon-audience {
      top: 40px;
      right: -40px;
      width: 280px;
      height: 280px;
    }

    .audience-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    @media (min-width: 600px) {
      .audience-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }
    }

    @media (min-width: 900px) {
      .audience-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .audience-card {
      background: var(--white);
      padding: 32px 28px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
    }

    .audience-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(4, 25, 60, 0.08);
    }

    .audience-icon {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      display: block;
    }

    .audience-card h3 {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: var(--navy);
    }

    .audience-card p {
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      color: rgba(4, 25, 60, 0.6);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* ===== PROČ MY ===== */
    #why {
      background: var(--white);
      padding: 100px 0 110px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    #why .polygon-why {
      bottom: -60px;
      left: -80px;
      width: 320px;
      height: 320px;
    }

    .why-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 60px;
      align-items: start;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      .why-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 80px;
      }
    }

    .why-stats {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 36px;
    }

    .why-stat {
      border-left: 3px solid var(--red);
      padding-left: 24px;
    }

    .why-stat .big {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--navy);
      line-height: 1.1;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .why-stat p {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: rgba(4, 25, 60, 0.6);
    }

    .why-quote {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .why-quote blockquote {
      font-family: 'Sanchez', serif;
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 3vw, 1.7rem);
      color: var(--navy);
      line-height: 1.55;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .why-quote blockquote::before {
      content: '\201E';
      display: block;
      font-size: 4rem;
      color: var(--red);
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-family: 'Gabarito', sans-serif;
    }

    .why-quote cite {
      font-style: normal;
      font-family: 'Gabarito', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: rgba(4, 25, 60, 0.5);
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    /* ===== FORMÁTY ===== */
    #formats {
      background: var(--navy);
      color: var(--white);
      padding: 100px 0 110px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    #formats .polygon-formats {
      top: -60px;
      right: -100px;
      width: 300px;
      height: 300px;
    }

    .formats-list {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 60px;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      .formats-list {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        gap: 32px;
      }
    }

    .format-item {
      padding: 32px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(201, 232, 251, 0.12);
      border-radius: 12px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      transition: border-color 0.3s;
    }

    .format-item:hover {
      border-color: rgba(201, 232, 251, 0.3);
    }

    .format-tag {
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--orange);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .format-item h3 {
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .format-item p {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .formats-note {
      text-align: center;
      font-family: 'Sanchez', serif;
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    /* ===== KONTAKT ===== */
    #contact {
      background: var(--white);
      padding: 100px 0 110px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    #contact .polygon-contact {
      top: -40px;
      right: -60px;
      width: 260px;
      height: 260px;
    }

    .contact-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 60px;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      .contact-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 80px;
      }
    }

    .contact-info h2 {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }

    .contact-info p {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      color: rgba(4, 25, 60, 0.6);
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      max-width: 440px;
    }

    .contact-direct {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .contact-direct a {
      color: var(--navy);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1rem;
      transition: color 0.2s;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .contact-direct a:hover {
      color: var(--red);
    }

    .contact-direct .icon {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      background: var(--light-blue);
      border-radius: 8px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .contact-form {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .form-group {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .form-group label {
      display: block;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--navy);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .form-group input,
    .form-group textarea {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      border: 2px solid rgba(4, 25, 60, 0.1);
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-family: 'Gabarito', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--navy);
      background: var(--white);
      transition: border-color 0.25s;
      outline: none;
    }

    .form-group input:focus,
    .form-group textarea:focus {
      border-color: var(--red);
    }

    .form-group textarea {
      resize: vertical;
      min-height: 120px;
    }

    .form-submit {
      width: 100%;
    }

    /* ===== FOOTER ===== */
    footer {
      background: var(--navy);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
      padding: 48px 0;
    }

    .footer-inner {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 20px;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      .footer-inner {
        flex-direction: row;
        justify-content: space-between;
        text-align: left;
      }
    }

    .footer-brand {
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      color: var(--white);
    }

    .footer-brand span {
      color: var(--red);
    }

    .footer-meta {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .footer-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .footer-links a {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }

    .footer-links a:hover {
      color: var(--white);
    }

    .powered-by {
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 32px;
      margin-top: 32px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    }

    /* ===== RESPONSIVE TWEAKS ===== */
    @media (max-width: 767px) {
      #hero {
        padding: 120px 0 80px;
        min-height: auto;
      }

      .section-heading {
        margin-bottom: 40px;
      }

      .why-quote blockquote {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
      }

      .audience-grid {
        gap: 16px;
      }
    }

    /* ===== MISC ===== */
    ::selection {
      background: var(--red);
      color: var(--white);
    }

    /* Smooth transition for anchors */
    a {
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ===== NAV ===== -->
<nav class="nav" id="nav">
  <div class="container">
    <a href="#hero" class="nav-logo">generace<span>.</span>work</a>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="#problem">Problém</a></li>
      <li><a href="#pillars">Nabídka</a></li>
      <li><a href="#why">Proč my</a></li>
      <li><a href="#formats">Formáty</a></li>
      <li><a href="#contact" class="nav-cta">Kontakt</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- ===== 1. HERO ===== -->
<section id="hero">
  <!-- Polygon decorations -->
  <div class="polygon polygon-hero-1">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 400 400" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <polygon points="200,20 380,150 340,370 60,370 20,150" fill="rgba(201,232,251,0.06)" stroke="rgba(201,232,251,0.12)" stroke-width="1"/>
    </svg>
  </div>
  <div class="polygon polygon-hero-2">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 300 300" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <polygon points="150,10 290,90 270,270 30,270 10,90" fill="rgba(201,232,251,0.04)" stroke="rgba(201,232,251,0.1)" stroke-width="1"/>
    </svg>
  </div>
  <div class="polygon polygon-hero-3">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <polygon points="100,5 195,65 170,185 30,185 5,65" fill="rgba(201,232,251,0.05)" stroke="rgba(201,232,251,0.1)" stroke-width="1"/>
    </svg>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <span class="hero-tag">generace.work</span>
      <h1>Rozumíme generaci,<br>kterou <span class="accent">potřebujete.</span></h1>
      <p>Pomáháme firmám najít, udržet a vést mladé zaměstnance. 15 let dat. Tisíce proškolených lidí. Nejlepší Gen&nbsp;Z data v&nbsp;Česku.</p>
      <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary">Chci vědět víc</a>
    </div>
  </div>
